    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.84) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.92)) * wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.15)))
    tmp = ((0.42 * v0) * ((v0 + 0.24 + v0 + 0.17) - (v0 + 0.74 / v2 + 0.00)))
    v1 = ((tmp + v2) + ((v0 + 0.92 + v0 + 0.50) + (v1 + 0.59 / tmp + 0.04)))
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.81) + wp.sin(tmp + 0.69)) * ((tmp + 0.73 * tmp + 0.84) / 0.26))
    data[tid] = v0
